snippet.textDisplay: I am big fan of coke studio and my Pakistani talent, but this 2nd episode is completely bull shit, all songs are average below regardless of big artists. I think coke studio organizers are in pride and delusion, where they think people only see big so called artists and not pay attention to the quality of songs and poetry, but they are wrong. In 1950, 60, and 70 Pakistani legend composers had competitions with big industry in India and they composed such a master pieces. I think coke studio Pakistan this time is not fully prepared and they only fill the blanks, not quality which was the strength of Pakistani coke studio. they must not compromise the quality, and delay the show until they find the right singers with right songs. They must not rely on big so called artists rather than open the competition and allow all artists from Pakistan to bring new ideas and new talent. Overall I am very disappointed season 2 especially and hope they not repeat it for coming episodes.
